09:20:58,980 --> 09:21:01,379
Is that what you see, move?

15588
09:21:01,440 --> 09:21:01,559
Moon?

15589
09:21:01,680 --> 09:21:04,559
Not exactly, she said.

15590
09:21:04,620 --> 09:21:06,239
The vision I see.

15591
09:21:06,300 --> 09:21:09,180
I don't think you'd be able to see it.

15592
09:21:09,239 --> 09:21:11,400
He raised his head and looked offended.

15593
09:21:11,459 --> 09:21:13,080
Oh, really?

15594
09:21:13,139 --> 09:21:14,940
You can see a future, I can't.

15595
09:21:15,000 --> 09:21:17,639
I think so, she said.

15596
09:21:17,699 --> 09:21:19,260
