15597
09:21:19,319 --> 09:21:21,300
It's a vision of a dragonette.

15598
09:21:21,360 --> 09:21:23,339
He's growing up in the rainforest.

15599
09:21:23,400 --> 09:21:26,040
He loves to weave and fish and sing.

15600
09:21:26,099 --> 09:21:29,220
His favorite fruit is strawberries, which

15601
09:21:29,220 --> 09:21:30,900
he and his friends fly to the mountains

15602
09:21:30,900 --> 09:21:31,319
to find.

15603
09:21:31,379 --> 09:21:34,680
He teaches himself to make jam and pies

15604
09:21:34,680 --> 09:21:37,620
and he writes a song called strawberries

15605
09:21:37,620 --> 09:21:40,019
as big as a scavenger's head, which

15606
09:21:40,019 --> 09:21:41,519
becomes the anthem for a yearly

15607
09:21:41,519 --> 09:21:42,419
strawberry festival.

15608
09:21:42,480 --> 09:21:45,900
He lives a peaceful, ordinary life.

15609
09:21:45,959 --> 09:21:49,080
He marries the tribe's blacksmith, and

15610
09:21:49,080 --> 09:21:51,540
they have 2 funny little dragonettes, who

15611
09:21:51,540 --> 09:21:53,339
steal his strawberries and make him laugh

15612
09:21:53,339 --> 09:21:53,940
every day.

15613
09:21:54,000 --> 09:21:57,839
They're with him when he dies quietly in

15614
09:21:57,839 --> 09:21:58,319
his sleep.

15615
09:21:58,379 --> 09:22:02,099
She paused, watching him expectantly.

15616
09:22:02,160 --> 09:22:06,419
Well, I don't know who that is, he said.

15617
09:22:06,480 --> 09:22:08,879
She kept looking at him and he frowned.

15618
09:22:08,940 --> 09:22:12,239
I mean, who loves strawberries that

15619
09:22:12,239 --> 09:22:12,480
much?

15620
09:22:12,540 --> 09:22:13,919
I've never tried one.

15621
09:22:13,980 --> 09:22:15,900
They look like they're full of seeds.

15622
09:22:15,959 --> 09:22:17,879
Really?

15623
09:22:18,000 --> 09:22:19,739
Moon said with a little laugh.

15624
09:22:19,800 --> 09:22:21,360
They're not at all.

15625
09:22:21,419 --> 09:22:22,440
You'd like them?

15626
09:22:22,500 --> 09:22:24,959
I saw some over here.

15627
09:22:25,019 --> 09:22:27,959
Those layers said, searching a patch of

15628
09:22:27,959 --> 09:22:29,160
leaves near her talons.

15629
09:22:29,279 --> 09:22:31,680
She plucked one of the dark, jewel red

15630
09:22:31,680 --> 09:22:33,419
fruits and passed it to her son.

15631
09:22:33,419 --> 09:22:36,000
He held the green stem between his claws

15632
09:22:36,000 --> 09:22:37,800
and eyed it suspiciously.

15633
09:22:37,860 --> 09:22:40,139
Wait, he said.

15634
09:22:40,199 --> 09:22:42,720
You think the dragon in your vision is

15635
09:22:42,720 --> 09:22:43,019
me.

15636
09:22:43,139 --> 09:22:48,239
You, without your powers, said Moon, you

15637
09:22:48,239 --> 09:22:51,300
without your memories, a new you, with a

15638
09:22:51,300 --> 09:22:52,199
chance to start over.

15639
09:22:52,260 --> 09:22:54,779
Dark Stalker snorted.

15640
09:22:54,839 --> 09:22:57,059
Little puffs of flame shooting out of his

15641
09:22:57,059 --> 09:22:57,300
nose.

15642
09:22:57,360 --> 09:23:00,720
Why would I ever give up my powers?

15643
09:23:00,720 --> 09:23:01,500
he said.

15644
09:23:01,620 --> 09:23:04,800
I'm the most powerful dragon Pyria has

15645
09:23:04,800 --> 09:23:05,099
ever seen.

15646
09:23:05,160 --> 09:23:07,260
Everyone wants to be me.

15647
09:23:07,319 --> 09:23:10,620
I don't, said Kibley.

15648
09:23:10,680 --> 09:23:13,319
Me neither, said Kinkachu.

15649
09:23:13,379 --> 09:23:16,199
Evil and smug and fat headed and evil.

15650
09:23:16,260 --> 09:23:16,860
No, thank you.

15651
09:23:16,919 --> 09:23:21,540
I'm not, Dark Stalker started, and then

15652
09:23:21,540 --> 09:23:23,279
surprisingly, fell silent.

15653
09:23:23,339 --> 09:23:26,879
Beauslayer settled her tail over his, and

15654
09:23:26,879 --> 09:23:29,099
patted one of his free talons, as though

15655
09:23:29,099 --> 09:23:30,300
it was a lonely sloth.

15656
09:23:30,360 --> 09:23:33,660
You could be happy, she said to him.

15657
09:23:33,720 --> 09:23:35,459
You could be loved.

15658
09:23:35,519 --> 09:23:38,940
But you have to choose it, Moon said.

15659
09:23:39,000 --> 09:23:40,800
You're the only one who can make it

15660
09:23:40,800 --> 09:23:41,099
real.

15661
09:23:41,160 --> 09:23:43,440
Imagine it, dark stalker.

15662
09:23:43,500 --> 09:23:45,300
If you turn yourself into a different

15663
09:23:45,300 --> 09:23:45,959
dragon.

15664
09:23:46,019 --> 09:23:48,000
You could actually do good things for the

15665
09:23:48,000 --> 09:23:48,239
world.

15666
09:23:48,360 --> 09:23:50,940
He shook his head vigorously.

15667
09:23:51,000 --> 09:23:52,860
That's ridiculous.

15668
09:23:52,919 --> 09:23:54,480
Without my powers.

15669
09:23:54,540 --> 09:23:55,860
What do I do?

15670
09:23:55,919 --> 09:23:57,000
Make pie.

15671
09:23:57,059 --> 09:23:58,379
You must be joking.

15672
09:23:58,500 --> 09:24:00,900
Couldn't I do more good things with my

15673
09:24:00,900 --> 09:24:01,919
