15674
09:24:01,980 --> 09:24:02,699
He asked.

15675
09:24:02,819 --> 09:24:06,360
Like, take Pyrea into the glorious future

15676
09:24:06,360 --> 09:24:07,019
I've seen.

15677
09:24:07,139 --> 09:24:11,099
I'd rather have pie, Hinkachu said.

15678
09:24:11,160 --> 09:24:13,080
Moon shook her head.

15679
09:24:13,139 --> 09:24:15,839
The future of Pyria is not your own

15680
09:24:15,839 --> 09:24:18,419
personal scroll, waiting for you to write

15681
09:24:18,419 --> 09:24:19,500
it, Dark Stalker.

15682
09:24:19,559 --> 09:24:23,339
The only future you control is yours, and

15683
09:24:23,339 --> 09:24:24,779
you have not brought happiness to the

15684
09:24:24,779 --> 09:24:25,620
dragon tribes.

15685
09:24:25,680 --> 09:24:29,040
We don't want that future you see if we

15686
09:24:29,040 --> 09:24:30,660
have to travel your dark path to get

15687
09:24:30,660 --> 09:24:30,900
there.

15688
09:24:30,959 --> 09:24:34,080
Dark Stalker spun the strawberry in his

15689
09:24:34,080 --> 09:24:35,819
claws for a moment, thinking.

15690
09:24:36,000 --> 09:24:39,599
Do it, Thoslayer said quietly.

15691
09:24:39,660 --> 09:24:42,120
Become a dragonette again.

15692
09:24:42,180 --> 09:24:43,739
I'll take care of you.

15693
09:24:43,800 --> 09:24:45,180
I want to.

15694
09:24:45,239 --> 09:24:46,980
We'll be happy this time.

15695
09:24:47,040 --> 09:24:52,319
All I see this way is darkness. he said

15696
09:24:52,319 --> 09:24:53,459
touching his forehead.

15697
09:24:53,519 --> 09:24:57,000
Darkness is all the rest of us see.

15698
09:24:57,059 --> 09:25:00,239
If you do become king, Moon said, but

15699
09:25:00,239 --> 09:25:00,599
this way.

15700
09:25:00,720 --> 09:25:02,699
No, he said.

15701
09:25:02,760 --> 09:25:03,720
I can't.

15702
09:25:03,779 --> 09:25:04,379
I can't do it.

15703
09:25:04,440 --> 09:25:04,919
I won't.

15704
09:25:05,040 --> 09:25:07,800
Moon blinked, looking bewildered.

15705
09:25:07,860 --> 09:25:09,360
But my vision.

15706
09:25:09,419 --> 09:25:11,639
I'm sure this is the path you choose.

15707
09:25:11,699 --> 09:25:15,120
Dark Stalker's tail lashed back and forth

15708
09:25:15,120 --> 09:25:16,379
throwing off his mother's.

15709
09:25:16,440 --> 09:25:18,959
I don't want to lose all my memories.

15710
09:25:19,019 --> 09:25:20,639
I'd forget clear sight.

15711
09:25:20,699 --> 09:25:23,279
She'd be even more gone than she is now.

15712
09:25:23,339 --> 09:25:25,139
He rose to his feet.

15713
09:25:25,199 --> 09:25:28,260
No, I'm going to be king.

15714
09:25:28,379 --> 09:25:31,139
King of the whole continent, king of all

15715
09:25:31,139 --> 09:25:31,739
the tribes.

15716
09:25:31,800 --> 09:25:33,059
That's my future.

15717
09:25:33,120 --> 09:25:35,099
I've seen it a 1000 times.

15718
09:25:35,160 --> 09:25:37,739
Dark Stalker, please.

15719
09:25:37,800 --> 09:25:38,879
Moon pleaded.

15720
09:25:38,940 --> 09:25:40,620
I know there's good in you still.

15721
09:25:40,739 --> 09:25:43,319
If you listen to it, you'll choose this

15722
09:25:43,319 --> 09:25:45,059
for yourself, I'm sure you will.

15723
09:25:45,180 --> 09:25:48,900
You are a bunch of small minded little

15724
09:25:48,900 --> 09:25:51,720
lizards, he said, rising to his full

15725
09:25:51,720 --> 09:25:53,339
height and spreading his wings.

15726
09:25:53,400 --> 09:25:55,019
What did you think?

15727
09:25:55,080 --> 09:25:58,559
I'd taste a strawberry and decide, mmm

15728
09:25:58,559 --> 09:26:00,779
wow, that's worth giving up my magic

15729
09:26:00,779 --> 09:26:01,139
for.

15730
09:26:01,199 --> 09:26:04,440
He looked down at the tiny fruit in his

15731
09:26:04,440 --> 09:26:06,360
claws and ripped off all the green

15732
09:26:06,360 --> 09:26:06,839
leaves.

15733
09:26:06,900 --> 09:26:09,900
Or did you have turtle enchant this?

15734
09:26:10,019 --> 09:26:13,199
Or perhaps another secret animus I don't

15735
09:26:13,199 --> 09:26:13,440
know about?

15736
09:26:13,500 --> 09:26:14,879
It doesn't matter.

15737
09:26:14,940 --> 09:26:18,239
You boring, ordinary creatures.

15738
09:26:18,300 --> 09:26:20,519
I can't be enchanted by anyone.

15739
09:26:20,580 --> 09:26:21,900
I'm smarter now.

15740
09:26:22,019 --> 09:26:24,120
I've made myself completely safe.

15741
09:26:24,180 --> 09:26:27,959
Nobody's animus magic will work on me

15742
09:26:27,959 --> 09:26:30,599
which means nobody will ever be able to

15743
09:26:30,599 --> 09:26:31,260
stop me.

15744
09:26:31,319 --> 09:26:34,080
He threw the strawberry in its mouth and

15745
09:26:34,080 --> 09:26:34,620
swallowed it.

15746
09:26:34,680 --> 09:26:36,660
Casting a dark look at his mother.

15747
09:26:36,720 --> 09:26:39,779
Actually, said Kinkaju.

15748
09:26:39,900 --> 09:26:42,419
There is one dragon's magic that will

15749
09:26:42,419 --> 09:26:43,260
still work on you.

15750
09:26:43,319 --> 09:26:45,779
He glowered down at her.

15751
09:26:45,839 --> 09:26:47,400
You're wrong.

15752
09:26:47,459 --> 09:26:50,639
I'm right, she snapped back.

15753
09:26:50,699 --> 09:26:51,839
Oh, really?

15754
09:26:51,900 --> 09:26:52,980
Whose?

15755
09:26:53,099 --> 09:26:55,980
She glared right back, and her scales

15756
09:26:55,980 --> 09:26:58,620
were the color of burning strawberries.

15757
09:26:58,680 --> 09:26:59,879
Your own.

15758
09:27:00,000 --> 09:27:04,379
Chapter 31.

15759
09:27:04,620 --> 09:27:08,760
Kinkaju upended her pouch and poured a

15760
09:27:08,760 --> 09:27:10,919
tiny pile of scraps of paper onto the

15761
09:27:10,919 --> 09:27:11,760
ground in front of her.

15762
09:27:11,819 --> 09:27:14,400
Kibley's mouth dropped open.

15763
09:27:14,459 --> 09:27:18,480
The last pieces of Dark Stalker's scroll

15764
09:27:18,480 --> 09:27:21,720
the ones chameleon used to transform

15765
09:27:21,720 --> 09:27:23,040
himself into different dragons.

15766
09:27:23,160 --> 09:27:26,819
He could see the dark, jagged scrawl of

15767
09:27:26,819 --> 09:27:29,339
Parel's father's handwriting on them.

15768
09:27:29,400 --> 09:27:31,739
And then, as Kinkachu carefully flipped

15769
09:27:31,739 --> 09:27:34,379
them over, he recognized her own awkward

15770
09:27:34,379 --> 09:27:36,599
lettering on the other side, and he

15771
09:27:36,599 --> 09:27:38,760
remembered the hours and hours she'd

15772
09:27:38,760 --> 09:27:41,220
spent practicing so she could be the 1st

15773
09:27:41,220 --> 09:27:43,019
rain wing in a century to learn to

15774
09:27:43,019 --> 09:27:43,260
write.

15775
09:27:43,319 --> 09:27:46,620
She used his own magic against him.

15776
09:27:46,680 --> 09:27:48,059
What?

15777
09:27:48,120 --> 09:27:50,639
Dog stalker said, choking.

15778
09:27:50,699 --> 09:27:51,779
But how?

15779
09:27:51,839 --> 09:27:53,099
I didn't see.

15780
09:27:53,160 --> 09:27:54,540
I know.

15781
09:27:54,599 --> 09:27:57,540
Kinkachu said proudly, never saw me

15782
09:27:57,540 --> 09:28:00,239
coming, taken down by a ball of fluff.

15783
09:28:00,300 --> 09:28:03,180
Who's insignificant now, frog face?

15784
09:28:03,239 --> 09:28:05,879
Dark soccer collapsed forward.

15785
09:28:05,940 --> 09:28:09,599
No, he was shrinking, Kibley realized.

15786
09:28:09,660 --> 09:28:11,760
You knew?

15787
09:28:11,879 --> 09:28:13,440
He gasped to his mother.

15788
09:28:13,500 --> 09:28:14,819
You helped her.

15789
09:28:14,879 --> 09:28:17,760
Of course I did, she said.

15790
09:28:17,819 --> 09:28:19,199
What else could I do?

15791
09:28:19,260 --> 09:28:20,760
Send you to your room?

15792
09:28:20,819 --> 09:28:22,680
Extra chores for week?

15793
09:28:22,739 --> 09:28:25,319
Somehow, neither of those seemed

15794
09:28:25,319 --> 09:28:27,300
particularly apt for this situation.

15795
09:28:27,360 --> 09:28:29,519
She patted his shoulder.

15796
09:28:29,580 --> 09:28:32,339
He was now about the same size as her.

15797
09:28:32,400 --> 09:28:36,419
It was this, or leave forever, and never

15798
09:28:36,419 --> 09:28:36,959
see you again.

15799
09:28:37,080 --> 09:28:40,440
I decided we'd both be happier this way.

15800
09:28:40,500 --> 09:28:44,400
But my powers, he cried.

15801
09:28:44,459 --> 09:28:47,279
His voice was higher, less cavernous and

15802
09:28:47,279 --> 09:28:49,980
booming now, as his lungs shrank.

15803
09:28:50,040 --> 09:28:51,000
All my magic.

15804
09:28:51,059 --> 09:28:52,800
Can't I keep any of it?

15805
09:28:52,860 --> 09:28:54,239
The mind reading?

15806
09:28:54,300 --> 09:28:54,599
Wait.

15807
09:28:54,660 --> 09:28:57,720
Dark soccer held up his front talons

15808
09:28:57,720 --> 09:28:59,400
watching the claws get smaller.

15809
09:28:59,459 --> 09:29:02,819
Sorry, Dark Stalker, Hibley said.

15810
09:29:02,879 --> 09:29:05,339
You had more than one chance to use them

15811
09:29:05,339 --> 09:29:07,620
wisely and well, and you chose not to.

15812
09:29:07,680 --> 09:29:10,319
I really thought he was going to choose

15813
09:29:10,319 --> 09:29:13,500
this for himself, Moon said, tipping her

15814
09:29:13,500 --> 09:29:14,639
head at the shrinking dragon.

15815
09:29:14,699 --> 09:29:18,779
Oh, I knew he wouldn't, Kinkachu said, but

15816
09:29:18,779 --> 09:29:20,699
I couldn't tell you my awesome plan

15817
09:29:20,699 --> 09:29:20,940
obviously.

15818
09:29:21,000 --> 09:29:23,220
You told her, though.

15819
09:29:23,279 --> 09:29:25,500
Why didn't he see it in your mind?

15820
09:29:25,559 --> 09:29:27,660
Moon asked Foeslayer.

15821
09:29:27,720 --> 09:29:30,540
You don't raise a mind reading sun

15822
09:29:30,540 --> 09:29:32,699
without learning a few tricks about how

15823
09:29:32,699 --> 09:29:35,160
to hide your thoughts, those slayers said

15824
09:29:35,160 --> 09:29:37,739
calmly, Didn't I help you?

15825
09:29:37,860 --> 09:29:41,519
Dark Stalker said. in a lost, small voice

15826
09:29:41,519 --> 09:29:42,839
looking up at Moon.

15827
09:29:42,900 --> 09:29:45,120
Didn't I save dragons too?

15828
09:29:45,180 --> 09:29:46,500
I'm not evil.

15829
09:29:46,559 --> 09:29:47,400
I'm not.

15830
09:29:47,459 --> 09:29:50,339
Not anymore, Kinkaju said.

15831
09:29:50,459 --> 09:29:52,500
As a shimmer spread across his scales.

15832
09:29:52,559 --> 09:29:55,919
Dark stalker was a dragonette now, younger

15833
09:29:55,919 --> 09:29:58,440
than anemone, and then younger still

15834
09:29:58,440 --> 09:30:00,360
until he appeared to be about one year

15835
09:30:00,360 --> 09:30:00,720
old.

15836
09:30:00,779 --> 09:30:04,319
He lifted his wings awkwardly, and Kibley

15837
09:30:04,319 --> 09:30:06,779
noticed that the line of white ice wing

15838
09:30:06,779 --> 09:30:08,400
scales was gone from under his wings.

15839
09:30:08,459 --> 09:30:11,160
But he wasn't entirely black either.

15840
09:30:11,220 --> 09:30:13,980
Underneath his wings, in place of the

15841
09:30:13,980 --> 09:30:16,919
usual night wing silver star scales, he

15842
09:30:16,919 --> 09:30:19,199
had a constellation of rainbow colored

15843
09:30:19,199 --> 09:30:22,559
scales, one emerald green here, one

15844
09:30:22,559 --> 09:30:25,739
parrot blue there, sunrise gold, and

15845
09:30:25,739 --> 09:30:27,480
oranges scattered throughout the black

15846
09:30:27,480 --> 09:30:30,540
scales, like shining beetles dropped on a

15847
09:30:30,540 --> 09:30:31,440
dark velvet cloth.

15848
09:30:31,500 --> 09:30:33,959
What in the world?

15849
09:30:34,019 --> 09:30:35,040
Moon asked.

15850
09:30:35,099 --> 09:30:38,220
Oh, yeah, I made him half rain wing

15851
09:30:38,220 --> 09:30:40,800
Kinkaju said, fighting back a giggle.

15852
09:30:40,860 --> 09:30:43,019
I thought that would be good for him, and

15853
09:30:43,019 --> 09:30:44,339
it turned out so pretty.

15854
09:30:44,400 --> 09:30:47,400
I'll work it into my backstory.

15855
09:30:47,459 --> 09:30:49,440
